#: src/mathlib.c:1047
#, c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"* Notice: \"%s\" was selected, but you can only change to a\n"
"* different Intel MKL threading library by restarting xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* However, you may continue to select any other Linear Algebra library\n"
"* without restart, including this same Intel MKL library.  All other\n"
"* Intel MKL threading libraries are disabled until restart because of an \n"
"* MKL limitation where the MKL threading library can only be dynamically\n"
"* linked only once per runtime.\n"
"* \n"
"* See Intel's documentation on mkl_set_threading_layer() for more detail.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"* Napomena: Odabran je \"%s\", ali možete preći samo na drugu\n"
"* Intel MKL threading biblioteku ponovnim pokretanjem xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* Međutim, možete nastaviti odabirati bilo koju drugu biblioteku linearne\n"
"* algebre bez ponovnog pokretanja, uključujući ovu istu Intel MKL "
"biblioteku.\n"
"* Sve ostale Intel MKL threading biblioteke su onemogućene do ponovnog\n"
"* pokretanja zbog MKL ograničenja gdje se MKL threading biblioteka može\n"
"* dinamički povezati samo jednom po pokretanju.\n"
"* \n"
"* Pogledajte Intel-ovu dokumentaciju o mkl_set_threading_layer() za "
"detalje.\n"

